<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī gaṇādhipatayē namaḥ namastuṁgaśiracuṁbicaṁdracāmaracāra
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vē trayilōkyanagarāraṁbhamūlastaṁbhāya śaṁbhavē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> harērlīlāvara
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hasya dauṣṭrādaṁḍassa pātu vaḥ hēmādri kalaśā yatra dhā trīchatraśriyaṁ
<lb n="4"/>dadhau <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī jayādbudayaśālivāhana śakavarṣa 1446 ne
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ya plavaṁga saṁvatsarada veyiśākha <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>rājādhirājaparamēśvara <unclear>śrī vīrapratāpa kṛṣṇarāya</unclear> mahārā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>ju śākhādhyā
<lb n="9-12"/><ce>lines are completely worn out</ce>
</p>

